Parameters.Name: pLogOutput
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Write parameters and action summary to server message log (Boolean True = 1)

Parameters.Name: pStrictErrorHandling
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: On encountering any error, exit with major error status by ProcessQuit after writing to the server message log (Boolean True = 1)

Parameters.Name: pTgtDim
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Target Dimension (will default to pSrcDim_clone If blank (or) is same as pSrcDim)

Parameters.Name: pHier
Parameters.Prompt: REQUIRED: Hierarchies to be included (will use default is left blank), accepts wildcards (if = *, then all hierarchies)

Parameters.Name: pUnwind
Parameters.Prompt: REQUIRED: 0 = Delete all Elements, 1 = Unwind Existing Elements, 2 = Do not change Existing Elements

Parameters.Name: pDelim
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: delimiter character for element list (required if pEle parameter is used) (default value if blank = '&')
